# material PreviewMaterial preset matte.clay
# material PreviewMaterial preset plastic.gloss-white
# material PreviewMaterial preset glass.clear
# material PreviewMaterial preset metal.gold roughness 0.16

material PreviewMaterial preset metal.brushed-aluminum roughness 0.18
